Description: ==========================
        tzf.pyramid_yml README
        ==========================
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/fizyk/pyramid_yml.png?branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.org/fizyk/pyramid_yml
            :alt: Tests for RandomWords
        
